ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR HARDWARE DESIGNS
================================================================================

The hardware designs (PCB layouts, schematics, and 3D models) in this project
are licensed under the MIT License with the following additional terms:

1. FREEDOM TO USE
   - You are free to manufacture PCBs from the provided Gerber files
   - You may use this design for personal, educational, or commercial purposes
   - No permission needed to build or modify for your own use

2. ATTRIBUTION APPRECIATED (not required)
   - If you redistribute the design, please acknowledge the original designers
   - Link back to this repository if possible
   - Credit goes a long way in the maker community

3. NO WARRANTY
   - The designs are provided as-is without any warranty
   - Manufacturers are responsible for design verification
   - Component selection and safety are your responsibility
   - Test all devices before use

4. RESPONSIBLE USE
   - Follow local laws and regulations
   - Use only for legal purposes
   - Do not use for harm or illegal activities
   - Respect intellectual property of component manufacturers

5. COMPONENT LICENSING
   - Respect licenses of third-party components used
   - KiCAD is licensed under CERN Open Hardware License (COHL)
   - Libraries and symbols follow their respective licenses
   - See individual component datasheets for additional terms

6. SOFTWARE LICENSE
   - Firmware code is under MIT License
   - You may use, modify, and distribute freely
   - Provide source code when distributing modified versions
   - Include this license in distributions

