DISCLAIMER
================================================================================

SAFETY WARNING: This project involves working with:
- Electrical components and power supplies
- Soldering and high-temperature tools
- Lithium-based batteries (in battery variant)
- Radio frequency transmitters (WiFi)

Users are responsible for:
- Following proper safety procedures
- Using appropriate safety equipment
- Understanding electrical safety
- Proper battery handling and disposal
- Compliance with local regulations

The authors are NOT responsible for:
- Injuries or accidents during assembly
- Damage to property or equipment
- Improper use or misuse of the device
- Regulatory violations in your jurisdiction
- Battery fires or explosions from mishandling

BUILD AT YOUR OWN RISK

